    <h1>Colors</h1>
    <p class="text-m color-neutral-600">A neutral palette from near-white to near-black, semantic status colors, and two required brand tokens that consuming applications must supply.</p>
  </header>

  <section>
    <div class="flow" style="--flow-space: var(--space-s);">
      <h2 class="heading-l">Neutral palette</h2>
